---
title: Saffron Risotto with Herby Baked Tomatoes and Lemony Pea Shoot Salad
description: This vegetarian risotto is a collab recipe from chefs André and Lizzie, and it’s more than a little bit special. Double the chef power, double the deliciousness! The silky richness of this delicately spiced saffron risotto, works perfectly with herby baked vine tomato, fresh gremolata and a lemony pea shoot salad. For a dish that tastes as good as it looks, this recipe gets full marks.
